org.joyrest.context

Class DependencyInjectionConfigurer<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.joyrest.context.AbstractConfigurer<T>
      • org.joyrest.context.DependencyInjectionConfigurer<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Configurer<T>

    public abstract class DependencyInjectionConfigurer<T>
extends AbstractConfigurer<T>
    Abstract Configurer which is mainly used for an implementation of a new configurer that is based on some Dependency Injection Framework. Abstract class as a helper for initialization an ApplicationContext.
